                    <br /><br />This Price Concession:<br />
                    <ol class="a">
                        <li>is offered by the Zebra legal entity which may be accepting the purchase order related to this Price Concession, as it will be indicated on the associated purchase order acknowledgement that will be issued to you in due course;</li>
                        <li>is only made available to you, the purchasing entity identified in the field "Account";</li>                
                        <li>must be used only for the ultimate resale of the products listed herein to the End User identified above for the Opportunity detailed herein and may not be used for another transaction;</li>
                        <li>cannot be used in conjunction with other special pricing offers; and</li>
                        <li>is valid from the above-mentioned date, but Zebra may withdraw it at any time. For example, if the reseller does not pursue or win the transaction covered by this PC, or if it is superseded by a later price concession granted by Zebra for the same Opportunity.</li>
                        <li>The (recommended) pricing for the Zebra products and services offered for this Opportunity, are exclusive of all import and / or export duties and tariffs, all government value added, sales, use or other like taxes in force (including copyright levies if applicable) and any such duties, tariffs and taxes shall be assumed and paid for by the purchasing entity in addition to its payment hereof. Important: Zebra may adjust the (recommended) pricing set out herein during the validity period of this Price Concession, to recover Zebra’s increased costs arising out of or associated with the following (without limitations): (a) impact of tariffs, duties, and other governmental actions; (b) inflationary pressure, fluctuation in foreign currency exchange rates or other economic hardship; c) shortage of components beyond Zebra’s reasonable control (collectively (a)-(c) referred to herein as “Market Related Additional Charges”).Any dispute arising out of, or associated with the Market Related Additional Charges, that is not resolved within twenty (20) days, may trigger refusal to supply the products and/or services until the dispute is resolved. For the avoidance of doubt, Market
 Related Additional Charges will be included in the total (recommended) price set out herein.
                        </li>
                    </ol><br />If no Zebra services have been or will be offered or purchased in connection to this Price Concession, then you (and any other entities which may further resell the products related to this Price Concession) acknowledge that the products which may be supplied will not be supported by Zebra beyond the Zebra applicable standard warranty and that the end user may have no access to software and security updates.<br /><br />When the products listed herein are intended to replace Zebra devices that are currently in use by the End User (“Current Install Base”), you will inform the End User that Zebra may be interested in purchasing their Current Install Base, and that they should contact Zebra at buybacks@zebra.com to allow Zebra to bid on such products (the “Zebra Buy Back Option”). If you are not selling directly to an End User, you will ensure that the entity who does, informs the End User of the Zebra Buy-Back Option. Failure to comply with this requirement may put your company in ‘not in good standing’ status in the PartnerConnect Program.<br /><br />If the transaction related to this approval requires the products to be shipped for use outside the appointed region of the Authorised Distributor and/or Partner, Zebra reserves the right to terminate any approved Price Concession with immediate effect. 
<br/><br/>
Please include the Price Concession Request ID number above on any future related correspondence. If you have questions regarding this Price Concession, contact your Zebra Account Manager.<br /><br />Sincerely, <br/>
Zebra Technologies*<br /><br />*The Zebra Technologies legal entity which may be accepting the purchase order(s) associated with this Price Concession, under the terms and conditions of your agreement with such entity.<br /><br /><br /><br /> 
                    
